{"tid":776545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英引猶太大屠殺相比    前FCC委員斥引喻失義","createTime":"2018-08-12T07:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T12:02:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d352e3894bdbcc00ce31b4c7d233b15cd14d8bc0","tid":776545,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534058972_61be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534058972_61be.png&h=7817d90e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民族黨召集人陳浩天獲邀出席外國記者會（FCC）演講，引發前特首梁振英連日追擊。曾出任FCC執委23年、前香港電台資深政治記者Francis Moriarty在個人fb專頁，再與梁振英隔空駁火，以個人身分反駁梁振英。<br />\n<br />\nMoriarty批評，梁振英最新帖文引喻失義，以南京大屠殺及猶太大屠殺的錯誤例子企圖帶來誤導（dealing in false analogies that seek to mislead）。他指出，任何人都難以將一名20餘歲港獨支持者出席午餐會演講，與兩項大屠殺事件作類比。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534056608_1466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534056608_1466.jpg&h=15171258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內文指，猶太大屠殺是納粹德國推行的種族滅絕政策，至今仍然震驚世界，受難者包括數以百萬計的猶太人、吉卜賽人、同性戀者、工會成員、共產黨員、納粹的政敵，甚至殘障人士。<br />\n<br />\n至於南京大屠殺事件是日本皇軍在二戰期間，殘酷屠殺中國人及其他亞裔人士的暴行。外國記者會內的記者更不會對南京大屠殺無知，記者既曾報道過事件，外國記者會70多年前於重慶成立時，也曾為逃避日軍亦從南京撤到上海，再到重慶。他重申，企圖以大屠殺作為比喻的意圖是錯誤。<br />\n<br />\nMoriarty提醒梁振英，高舉種族主義會令人厭惡，不少國家有法例禁止仇恨言論（hate speech），但倡議獨立的政治主張並不類同於仇恨言論；獨立主張也非誹謗等，不受法律保障的言論。陳浩天的港獨立場至於仍在探討層面，根本未構成煽動暴力。<br />\n<br />\n他更奉勸梁振英，如想對活動進行審查必須提出具說服力的論據，而非用上錯誤比喻，而陳浩天會在外國記者會午餐會，向滿場賓客演講已是既定事實。他又指，已查過天文台的下周的天氣預報，「冇話嗰日個天會跌落嚟（no warning of falling skies）」。<br />\n<br />\n他最後再諷刺梁振英，指在他印象中的確有人曾觸碰紅線，以香港作為基地，意圖顛覆中國政府，那一個取得成功的人就是孫中山。他估計梁振英也會支持孫中山當年在香港所做的事。"},{"pid":"39c6e1345800dae309695f2f9547753d6e98cf03","tid":776545,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:40:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誰是納綷？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">聯合國已掌握中國於新疆設滅絕營(集中營/再教育營)囚禁300萬維吾爾人確實證據</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-rights-un/u-n-says-it-has-credible-reports-that-china-holds-million-uighurs-in-secret-camps-idUSKBN1KV1SU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-rights-un%2Fu-n-says-it-has-credible-reports-that-china-holds-million-uighurs-in-secret-camps-idUSKBN1KV1SU&d=JuWwQ8HBR92R197b3UYfJuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=8e444255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-rights-un%2Fu-n-says-it-has-credible-reports-that-china-holds-million-uighurs-in-secret-camps-idUSKBN1KV1SU&h=96fda740\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-rights-un/u-n-says-it-has-credible-reports-that-china-holds-million-uighurs-in-secret-camps-idUSKBN1KV1SU</a><br />\n<br />\nU.N. says it has credible reports that China holds million Uighurs in secret camp<br />\n<br />\nGENEVA (Reuters) - A United Nations human rights panel said on Friday that it had received many credible reports that 1 million ethnic Uighurs in China are held in what resembles a &ldquo;massive internment camp that is shrouded in secrecy.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\nGay McDougall, a member of the U.N. Committee on the Elimination of Racial Discrimination, cited estimates that 2 million Uighurs and Muslim minorities were forced into &ldquo;political camps for indoctrination&rdquo; in the western Xinjiang autonomous region.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We are deeply concerned at the many numerous and credible reports that we have received that in the name of combating religious extremism and maintaining social stability (China) has changed the Uighur autonomous region into something that resembles a massive internship camp that is shrouded in secrecy, a sort of &lsquo;no rights zone&rsquo;,&rdquo; she told the start of a two-day regular review of China&rsquo;s record, including Hong Kong and Macao.<br />\n<br />\nChina has said that Xinjiang faces a serious threat from Islamist militants and separatists who plot attacks and stir up tensions between the mostly Muslim Uighur minority who call the region home and the ethnic Han Chinese majority.<br />\n<br />\nA Chinese delegation of some 50 officials made no comment on her remarks at the Geneva session that is scheduled to continue on Monday."},{"pid":"a542321cc4e98e3f091f9ff30614896ef25b83e3","tid":776545,"uid":61279,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"689 係咪轉行做 kol，<br />\n成撚日喺 fb 9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09c19fdf128f421881908ecfb1c080f6a4806cc","tid":776545,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a542321cc4e98e3f091f9ff30614896ef25b83e3","tid":776545,"uid":61279,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"689 係咪轉行做 kol，<br />\n成撚日喺 fb 9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"可以去城邦電台, 同云伯散播精神病毒"},{"pid":"95b18d6588145bbfdeeb67c6e4289f40847d71af","tid":776545,"uid":34010,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"forward去德國領事館facebook問下佢地點睇"},{"pid":"8df7f1f4d5229598a8e2971fb257ff576b26b104","tid":776545,"uid":60366,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"一早話左依啲偷換概念嘅野就算呃到街邊啲人, 都呃唔到讀書人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fd29420e87a503f8cf2c0ad23468880fd723b5","tid":776545,"uid":127947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"馮萎光真係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=